name: ORBITRUNNER - Soundtoy 02
description:
An interactive sound toy developed with Unity in celebration of HEN600K.

Click on spheres to set notes and speed, the middle cube for the camera. Alternative keyboard controls are listed below; 
Key Up - Speed up
Key Down - Speed down
Key R - Reset speed
Space - Toggle Camera

Reminted for adaptive resolution feature, UI fix and added support for various mobile devices. Low performance on the first start is due to preloading audio assets for a seamless audio experience later on. Fullscreen is not effectively working on this platform, so token owners can request a PC or Mac build for the toy.
